Adminstration Assistant cum Accountant
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 16:12:01
Ref. JB2674608
Job Description
aramanstudio is a boutique photography and production studio based in Dubai with branches in Cairo and Beirut.
We are looking for a FEMALE Admin Assistant cum accountant with at least 2 or 3 years of experience.
This job is a multi-faceted, high paced job which requires a cross over of skills along with a strong accounting and presentation experience.
You will be the studio manager right hand person, willing to aid with everything from accounting, booking travel, responding to client questions, putting together presentations in Power Point, updating payment tracking, attending photoshoots when required, general errands and overall administrative/organizational work.
We are looking for someone to join our team that is highly energetic, great with high stress surroundings. She must have EXCELLENT English writing and speaking skills. She needs to be very presentable in the way she dresses and cares for herself, as the ideal candidate will be interacting with clients.
Flexibility on work schedule is a must.
Salary Range is from AED 3000- AED3500 per month (based on experience level) with yearly bonus of one month's salary.
Skills
Financial updates, tracking, accounts receivable/payable, data entry
Proficiency in Excel, Word, PowerPoint
Travel Booking, Schedule Management, Coordination of
Project, event management or logistics management skills
